CONTENT: Hello Peter,   My name is Josiah Mayo and I am a Recruiter w/ Insight Global in Bellevue, WA (nice to virtually meet you!) If you‚Äôre interested, please send your updated resume / the best time to connect on a call today or tomorrow! üòä The manager is looking to set up interviews as soon as possible.   Company: Microsoft Title: Product Manager Duration: 18 month contract Location: Redmond, WA (2-3 days onsite - flexible for days) Pay Rate: $45-$55/hr (possible flexibiity)  REQUIRED SKILLS AND EXPERIENCE GAME INDUSTRY EXPERIENCE Strong presentation, organization and Project/Product Management skills. CONTENT: Hi Peter,  Hope you are great. I wanted to connect and share something compelling in the music investment space. CONVERSATION TITLE: Diabetes Prevention Startup - Advisory Board Invitation
SUBJECT: Diabetes Prevention Startup - Advisory Board Invitation
CONTENT: Hello Peter,  I am the Vice President of Business Development of Fruit Street which is a leading digital health company that delivers a CDC-endorsed diabetes prevention program through telehealth and live group video conferencing with registered dietitians and wearable devices.   We are currently recruiting advisory board members who believe in our social mission of preventing diabetes via telehealth and thought you might be a great fit.   Responsibilities of advisors include:  -Giving input via email and Zoom with other advisors on the strategy and growth of the company. -Making helpful introductions to potential customers or partners. -Giving the management team guidance as they grow the venture.  Benefits to advisors include: -Being issued stock options in exchange for spending a few hours per month of your time on the company -Participating in Fruit Street's employee stock purchase plan (ESPP) which allows participating employees, advisors, and directors to buy company shares via an IRA/401K.   We are ideally looking for advisors that are interested in both advising and participating as an angel via the ESPP. Previous angel funding includes commitments of $35M from more than 500 physicians who have supported the company.   By preventing Type 2 diabetes via our digitally delivered program, we can help improve the health of the public by preventing diabetes related complications like amputation, blindness, stroke, heart disease, and early death. We can prevent a child from hearing that their parent died from a heart attack that was preventable.   If you are interested in being an advisor and would consider participating as an angel via the ESPP, please apply here: https://bit.ly/3LMQey4  Let me know your email / phone as well.  This is a deck about our company: https://hubs.ly/Q01Pcdhw0  Product video: https://bit.ly/42NQy7j  Best Regards, Dave Cubil Vice President for Business Development Fruitstreet Health

CONTENT: Hi Peter,  I hope you are doing well! A client of mine, Dashbot, is looking to bring on a Head of Product, so I wanted to see if you'd be interested in chatting.
